  "detailed_description": "Izeriya was a powerful city…but forces of evil captured it. The little man named Trix is heading to this city to destroy the evil within.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIn game you will pass obstacles and fight!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe game has a upgrade system, so you can upgrade the damage of your sword and fireballs, or you can upgrade your health and quantity of your mana.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIn game you will find three locations, and some extra levels!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIt won't be easy! You will kill a lot of monsters, to try not to die.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFight with hard bosses at the end of the locations!",
  "about_the_game": "Izeriya was a powerful city…but forces of evil captured it. The little man named Trix is heading to this city to destroy the evil within.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIn game you will pass obstacles and fight!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe game has a upgrade system, so you can upgrade the damage of your sword and fireballs, or you can upgrade your health and quantity of your mana.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIn game you will find three locations, and some extra levels!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIt won't be easy! You will kill a lot of monsters, to try not to die.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFight with hard bosses at the end of the locations!",
